{"title":"绿色的希望（外一首）","authors":["车美萍"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":5,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的希望（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车美萍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风携着细雨流进"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我灵魂深处的小窗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕子衔着软泥扑满"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我郁结许久的心房……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓦地，仿佛有滔滔春水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在我脉管里荡漾……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛，痒酥酥的温风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧起我那么多绿色的希望……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，春来了，绿了田野、山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要换一身绿色的新装……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睁开了绿色的眼睛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把一切都映绿了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青的湖，绿的树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在那绿毡子一般的平原上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦苗儿拔节，燕剪儿穿风……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切把我的心儿也染绿了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身飞涌着萌发的渴望！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把我撒进这黑色的沃土里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要发芽——不论在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥沃的良田，还是贫瘠的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土壤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，我的生命啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也正是早春时光！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}